1. what kind of search, search file name, file content

2. how do we search file? I mean the search conditions
path - from where we start search
~: user folder, .: current folder, ./a/b/c
file name - which file we want to search, is case sensitive or not,
            can it be regular expression by using question mark and star mark
file type - f: file, d:directory
file size - +50M, -100M
modify time - +50 -100
permission - read, write, execute
max depth - how deep does searching go

3. what kind information we need to return?
path that contains file name, modified date, owner, permission

4. Should the data sorted in a certain order?

